
This directory is intended for PlatformIO Test Runner and project tests.

Unit Testing is a software testing method by which individual units of
source code, sets of one or more MCU program modules together with associated
control data, usage procedures, and operating procedures, are tested to
determine whether they are fit for use. Unit testing finds problems early
in the development cycle.

More information about PlatformIO Unit Testing:
- https://docs.platformio.org/en/latest/advanced/unit-testing/index.html

## Judul Project
### “Implementasi Sistem Smart Building Berbasis IoT untuk Monitoring, Efisiensi Energi, dan Keamanan Ruangan”

## Konsep Sistem
Project ini adalah sistem smart building yang mampu:
memonitor kondisi ruangan realtime
menghemat energi otomatis
mendeteksi kondisi berbahaya
mengontrol perangkat dari jarak jauh
menampilkan dashboard monitoring berbasis web

## STACK SISTEM
1. Embedded System Layer
    Esp 32 Controler
2. Sensor Layer
    DHT 22
    PIR Motion Sensor
    LDR Sensor
    MQ-2 Smoke/Gas Sensor
3. Aktuator Layer
    A. Relay Modul
    B. DC fan 
    C. Servo Motor
    D. Buzzer
4. Communication Layer
    MQTT PROTOCOL 
        HiveMQ Public Broker
        atau:
        EMQX Public MQTT
5. Cloud / Database Layer
    Firebase Realtime Database
6. Dashboard Layer
    Custum dasboard usingg github Pages / blynk


## Feature:
Teknologi Dashboard
    Frontend
        HTML
        CSS
        JavaScript
    Visualisasi Data
        Chart.js

    Untuk:
        grafik realtime
        histori suhu
        konsumsi energi
    Fitur Dashboard
    Monitoring Realtime
        suhu
        kelembapan
        cahaya
        asap
        status ruangan
    Device Control
        lampu
        fan
        mode auto/manual


    System Status:
        ONLINE
        OFFLINE
        ALERT
        ECO MODE

7. Automation Layer
    Rule Automation
        Efisiensi Energi
            Jika ruangan kosong
            → lampu OFF
            → fan LOW POWER
        Smart Lighting
            Jika cahaya rendah dan ada orang
            → lampu ON
        Smart Cooling
            Jika suhu > 30°C
            → fan ON
        Safety System
            Jika asap terdeteksi
            → buzzer ON
            → dashboard ALERT

